Scenario: Checking the chat bot window conversation if the window screen is resized

Bug Description: Text box is not showing up if the window height is reduced

Browser: Chrome, Firefox

Environment: https://snatchbot.me/

User Permissions: Valid for all users

Steps to Reproduce: 
1. Navigate to url : https://snatchbot.me/
2. Click on chat bot icon
3. Reduce the height of window manually
4. Check the text box to type in message

Expected Behavior: Text Box should be displayed and enabled
Actual Behavior: Text box is not showing up if the window height is reduced

Impact: Medium
Priority: Medium

Attachments: Screenshot available with the name: Bug1-ScreenShot-testbox-is-not-showing-up